A graduate, Charles Olusegun Ajayi, popularly known as MC Gold, was on Monday killed by suspected cultists in Lokoja, Kogi State. Ajayi, a graduate of management from the Kogi State University, Anyigba, was a talented master of ceremony (MC), who had hosted and anchored several shows during his undergraduate years at the university. He was allegedly murdered by cultists around 12:00 a.m. on Monday. A source told the Nigerian Tribune that Ajayi, alongside his friend, Sunrich Aiyedogbon and two others were attacked at their residence in 200 Units, Lokoja, by suspected cultists numbering about 15. ALSO READ: Police kill notorious kidnapper, rescue victim in Katsina 12 persons kidnapped in Kogi, kidnappers demand N18m Commissioner tasks heads of institutions on eradicating… Kogi gov warns MDAs against contract inflation, projects… Two communities clash over fish ponds in Kogi as Egbura… Ajayi’s body was butchered with cutlass and axe, while his friends sustained serious injuries in the attack. The case was reported to the police and investigation is currently ongoing. Ajayi who is survived by parents, brother and sister were buried on Tuesday at the Lokongoma cemetery in Lokoja. Meanwhile, the state Commissioner for Education, Science and Technology, Mr Wemi Jones, has urged all heads of institutions in the state to intensify action in eradicating cultism in schools as directed by Governor Yahaya Bello. The commissioner gave the charge at the maiden meeting he held with education stakeholders in Lokoja. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY 